com.mashery.trafficmanager.model.core

Interface DeveloperClass


  • public interface DeveloperClass
    A mechanism to classify API Key that allows Traffic Manager to apply common processing logic to a group of keys. Each API Key may belong to at most one Developer Class
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be extended by clients.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getName()
      Returns the name of this Developer Class
      RateConstraint getRateConstraint()
      Returns this Developer Class' rate constraint, or null if none is configured on this Developer Class, or if the Endpoint does not allow overriding of rate constraints.
      ThrottleConstraint getThrottleConstraint()
      Returns this Developer Class' throttle constraint, or null if none is configured on this Developer Class, or if the Endpoint does not allow overriding of throttle constraints
      boolean isCallBlockingOn()
      Returns true if call blocking is currently in effect for this Developer Class
